title: [1508521049] The West House: Big Test - Gordon Ramsay
description:
Gordon Ramsay in search of Britain's best restaurant. Top restaurants from around the UK compete to win the title. 

British restaurant The West House, get put to the test by having to serve food in Gordon Ramsay's Restaurant, and impress 20 esteemed guests.
